curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/3512' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM13005M2", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM13005M2 is a low noise amplifier (LNA) with  bypass for LTE middle band receiving application. The  device features low noise figure and high linearity over a  supply voltage range from 1.5V to 3.6V. Low noise figure  improves the sensitivity of the SGM13005M2, and high  linearity enables the device to provide better immunity to  interference signals.  No external DC blocking capacitors are required on the  RF paths as long as no external DC voltage is applied,  which can save PCB area and cost.  The SGM13005M2 is available in a Green UTDFN-  1.1×0.7-6L package.    "}'
